                Aeliae <lb n="2"/>Prosperae <expan><abbr>c</abbr><ex>larissimi</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>f</abbr><ex>eminae</ex></expan> <lb n="3"/>coniugi <expan><abbr>C</abbr><ex>ai</ex></expan> <lb n="4"/>Pomponi Magni <lb n="5"/><expan><abbr>leg</abbr><ex>ati</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Aug<am>g</am></abbr><ex>ustorum</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>pr</abbr><ex>o</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>pr</abbr><ex>aetore</ex></expan> <lb n="6"/><expan><abbr>c</abbr><ex>larissimi</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>v</abbr><ex>iri</ex></expan> praesidis <lb n="7"/>stratores
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Datierung: Pomponius Magnus war entweder 210 bis 212 oder 244-249 n. Chr. Statthalter von Numidien.</p>
            </div>
